If I were to go with a propane cylinder that will be carried inside the bus
(as opposed to being attached to the exterior of the body), I would look at
something like this:

http://www.litecylinder.com/ourstory.aspx

http://www.amazon.com/Lite-Cylinder-LC-20-30-Composite-See-Through/dp/B000UWMJAM/ref=pd_cp_indust_0

Probably a little more money than the standard tank, but cheaper than a new
external tank from Go Westy!

